Class ElPollo.OverrideCustom<ObjType,ReturnType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.aqba.framework.elpollo.ElPollo.OverrideCustom<ObjType,ReturnType>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElPollo.OverrideCall
    Enclosing class:
    ElPollo

    public abstract static class ElPollo.OverrideCustom<ObjType,ReturnType>
extends java.lang.Object
    Used as an alternative to implement a custom method in the override class.
    Instances of this object MUST implement a call method matching the original method.

    Example:
    public void call(Object obj, int arg1, String arg2)
    See Also:
    ElPollo.MemberOverride, ElPollo.OverrideCall
